            <script>\n
                document.addEventListener('alpine:init', () => {\n
                    Alpine.data('projectIntro', () => ({\n
                        showIntro: true,\n
                        init() {\n
                            if (window.localStorage) {\n
                                this.showIntro = localStorage.getItem('project-wizard-intro') !== 'hidden';\n
                            }\n
                        },\n
                        dismissIntro(persist = false) {\n
                            this.showIntro = false;\n
                            if (persist && window.localStorage) {\n
                                localStorage.setItem('project-wizard-intro', 'hidden');\n
                            }\n
                        },\n
                    }));\n
        \n
                    Alpine.data('templatePanel', ({ templates = [] }) => ({\n
                        query: '',\n
                        templates,\n
                        get filtered() {\n
                            if (!this.query) {\n
                                return this.templates.slice(0, 100);\n
                            }\n
        \n
                            const needle = this.query.toLowerCase();\n
                            return this.templates\n
                                .filter((template) => {\n
                                    const haystacks = [\n
                                        template.name || '',\n
                                        template.headline || '',\n
                                        template.category || '',\n
                                        template.summary || '',\n
                                        ...(template.skills || []),\n
                                    ];\n
        \n
                                    return haystacks.some((value) => value && value.toLowerCase().includes(needle));\n
                                })\n
                                .slice(0, 100);\n
                        },\n
                    }));\n
                });\n
        \n
                document.addEventListener('livewire:load', () => {\n
                    document.body.classList.add('post-project-no-footer');\n
                    scrollAssistantToBottom();\n
                });\n
        \n
                document.addEventListener('beforeunload', () => {\n
                    document.body.classList.remove('post-project-no-footer');\n
                });\n
        \n
                document.addEventListener('livewire:navigated', (event) => {\n
                    const destination = event?.detail?.to?.url || window.location.href;\n
                    if (!destination.includes('post/project')) {\n
                        document.body.classList.remove('post-project-no-footer');\n
                    }\n
                });\n
        \n
                function scrollAssistantToBottom() {\n
                    const container = document.getElementById('assistantChatStream');\n
                    if (container) {\n
                        container.scrollTo({\n
                            top: container.scrollHeight,\n
                            behavior: 'smooth',\n
                        });\n
                    }\n
                }\n
        \n
                if (window.Livewire && typeof window.Livewire.hook === 'function') {\n
                    window.Livewire.hook('message.processed', () => {\n
                        scrollAssistantToBottom();\n
                    });\n
        \n
                    window.Livewire.on?.('project-template-applied', () => {\n
                        scrollAssistantToBottom();\n
                    });\n
                }\n
            </script>\n
